WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:07.220
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:07.220 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 26]

01:18.270 --> 01:20.420
On this mission, we must seize the Divine Tree's power

01:21.000 --> 01:22.340
and restore Dizang Sect's glory!

01:24.590 --> 01:26.030
[The Divine Tree emerges]

01:26.030 --> 01:27.420
Why does the Wuyue Court mobilize all forces

01:28.000 --> 01:29.780
to put Lifei on public trial

01:30.520 --> 01:31.140
before the Mountain and Sea Sects?

01:35.390 --> 01:35.890
Master,

01:36.550 --> 01:38.010
could they kill Lifei to grab

01:38.670 --> 01:39.940
the Divine Tree's power?

01:40.440 --> 01:42.010
From despair comes rebirth.

01:42.390 --> 01:44.220
There is surely sound sense

01:44.440 --> 01:45.730
in Mr. Zuo Qiu's arrangements.

01:46.160 --> 01:48.530
Let us wait and watch.

01:53.800 --> 01:55.370
Your Highness, what should we do now?

01:55.370 --> 01:56.080
[The Divine Tree emerges]

01:56.080 --> 01:58.140
Shall we gather men to rescue Lifei now?

02:03.640 --> 02:04.450
Did the Chufeng Academy

02:04.910 --> 02:06.290
leak this news?

02:07.310 --> 02:07.860
Yes.

02:32.240 --> 02:34.940
Heaven watches over us and protects our clan.

02:44.150 --> 02:46.060
I firmly believe Your Lordship will gain a new life.

02:46.760 --> 02:47.690
For five centuries,

02:47.920 --> 02:49.220
I snuck into the Wuyue Court countless times,

02:49.710 --> 02:51.690
only to search for Qingcheng and Your Lordship.

02:52.270 --> 02:53.740
Guangwei wounded me

02:54.200 --> 02:56.340
on my last try.

02:56.800 --> 02:58.250
Luckily, when his beloved disciple

02:58.270 --> 02:59.690
Yue Cailing chased me,

02:59.710 --> 03:00.650
I seized her mortal vessel.

03:01.670 --> 03:03.220
While recovering in Lugong Town,

03:03.870 --> 03:05.340
I finally awaited your return.

03:06.240 --> 03:07.650
This is great, my Lord.

03:07.800 --> 03:08.410
So,

03:11.590 --> 03:13.250
in the cave outside Lugong Town back then,

03:14.320 --> 03:15.460
you already knew who I was.

03:16.640 --> 03:17.850
You summoned the bone-devouring butterfly

03:18.430 --> 03:21.220
and made Songfeng fall into darkness, too.

03:23.990 --> 03:24.810
Lei Xiuyuan,

03:26.040 --> 03:27.220
how come you're conscious?

03:28.430 --> 03:29.940
You were poisoned by Soul-Bewitching Vines.

03:31.080 --> 03:32.130
Mere Soul-Bewitching Vines

03:33.150 --> 03:34.130
can never control me.

03:42.080 --> 03:43.970
I never intended to control you.

03:44.990 --> 03:47.370
I only hoped you'd remember you're Yecha.

03:47.390 --> 03:48.130
All I've ever been

03:49.270 --> 03:50.340
is Lei Xiuyuan.

03:50.870 --> 03:51.780
I don't understand.

03:51.960 --> 03:53.090
What joy is there in living as a human?

03:53.550 --> 03:55.940
Do you still dream of staying forever with the Divine Tree?

03:56.200 --> 03:57.060
I'm nothing like you.

03:59.550 --> 04:00.460
All I want is to live as a human,

04:01.760 --> 04:04.220
an ordinary man in this world.

04:06.990 --> 04:07.940
I made a promise to Lu,

04:09.040 --> 04:09.810
yet I broke it.

04:11.150 --> 04:11.900
This time,

04:12.870 --> 04:13.780
I'll not go back on my word.

04:14.710 --> 04:15.250
You!

04:15.800 --> 04:16.340
Rakshasa,

04:17.080 --> 04:18.780
you've caused trouble time and again.

04:19.520 --> 04:21.570
I cannot spare you any longer.

04:28.590 --> 04:30.010
Spare me, My Lord!

04:31.120 --> 04:32.420
Show mercy!

04:34.830 --> 04:35.540
Cuixuan

04:36.470 --> 04:38.330
has captured Jiang Lifei.

04:39.080 --> 04:40.980
They will destroy the Divine Tree.

04:41.680 --> 04:44.100
Just like a thousand years ago,

04:45.790 --> 04:48.450
they will tear her apart and feed on her power

04:50.080 --> 04:52.450
until her soul vanishes completely.

05:00.960 --> 05:01.620
My Lord!

05:30.320 --> 05:32.740
You claim to be the top cultivator of the immortal sects.

05:33.710 --> 05:36.330
Why do you need my master's Senluo Grand Art?

05:40.390 --> 05:41.370
I see.

05:42.520 --> 05:43.940
Without the miniature realm

05:44.760 --> 05:46.740
and the wronged demon spirit,

05:48.350 --> 05:50.210
you can never cultivate and ascend.

05:53.520 --> 05:54.980
Stop daydreaming.

05:56.120 --> 05:57.740
I'd rather die than give it to you.

06:00.320 --> 06:01.330
We'll see

06:02.470 --> 06:04.450
how tough you are.

06:20.470 --> 06:21.860
You imprisoned my master

06:23.150 --> 06:25.370
all for your greedy ambition.

06:25.590 --> 06:26.180
Silence!

06:27.640 --> 06:29.330
Everything I've done

06:29.880 --> 06:32.060
is for the immortal sects' grand cause.

06:34.120 --> 06:35.300
Absorbing demon spirits

06:36.350 --> 06:37.540
and slaying fellow cultivators

06:38.390 --> 06:40.100
are what you call the grand cause?

06:41.350 --> 06:44.860
If they saw you kill my master

06:45.590 --> 06:47.690
and piles of bones in the miniature realm,

06:48.830 --> 06:50.500
would they still buy your lies?

06:51.640 --> 06:53.660
The miniature realm has been destroyed.

06:54.230 --> 06:55.300
No one will believe a word

06:55.760 --> 06:57.130
of what you say.

06:57.910 --> 06:58.620
True,

07:00.320 --> 07:01.500
I have no proof.

07:02.560 --> 07:03.570
But my master once said

07:04.120 --> 07:05.690
justice prevails in this world.

07:08.710 --> 07:09.860
What justice?

07:10.120 --> 07:11.250
What even is justice?

07:12.030 --> 07:13.250
With the Fruit of the Divine Tree,

07:13.960 --> 07:16.180
I'll have endless spirit energy.

07:16.710 --> 07:18.420
Once my cultivation reaches perfection

07:18.760 --> 07:19.860
and I become an immortal,

07:21.000 --> 07:24.180
every word and deed of mine shall be the rules

07:24.200 --> 07:25.300
and the heavenly law itself.

07:28.520 --> 07:30.370
Your master is far too naive

07:30.880 --> 07:33.620
to still believe in karmic retribution.

07:33.640 --> 07:35.890
You have no right to mention him!

07:46.560 --> 07:47.540
Stop struggling.

07:48.470 --> 07:51.130
Even your master could not break these spirit-sealing chains,

07:51.790 --> 07:53.810
let alone you.

07:56.230 --> 07:57.180
Master.

08:00.590 --> 08:01.330
Don't move!

08:11.150 --> 08:13.660
You tricked my master back by using your bond

08:14.640 --> 08:15.660
as fellow disciples,

08:15.680 --> 08:18.500
locked him in the miniature realm, and tortured him.

08:19.200 --> 08:20.300
He was your senior brother.

08:21.080 --> 08:22.540
Do you have any conscience left?

08:22.680 --> 08:24.300
He wronged me first.

08:27.030 --> 08:28.890
Years ago, Yecha left me gravely wounded.

08:29.320 --> 08:30.660
As my fellow disciple,

08:31.790 --> 08:35.010
he refused to heal me with the Divine Tree and demon spirits,

08:35.790 --> 08:37.540
was obsessed with building the Outcast Tomb,

08:38.040 --> 08:39.730
and sealed all demon spirits away.

08:40.510 --> 08:41.940
Where

08:42.080 --> 08:44.780
was our bond back then?

08:46.230 --> 08:48.450
He was stopping you from falling into darkness.

08:48.560 --> 08:50.060
He fell into darkness!

08:50.350 --> 08:51.780
His heart belonged to foreign lands,

08:52.400 --> 08:53.540
and he betrayed our sect,

08:55.710 --> 08:59.730
leaving us his junior disciples to fend for ourselves.

09:01.040 --> 09:03.060
I trusted him with all my heart once,

09:03.710 --> 09:04.420
yet

09:05.440 --> 09:06.780
look what he did.

09:07.830 --> 09:09.300
He betrayed the sect.

09:10.080 --> 09:13.060
I hate how he cannot tell right from wrong.

09:13.560 --> 09:15.610
He never repented even till his last breath.

09:16.320 --> 09:17.690
Narrow-minded wretches

09:18.710 --> 09:20.970
will never understand embracing all beings,

09:20.990 --> 09:22.060
nor compassion for every living soul.

09:23.230 --> 09:24.210
All you see

09:24.920 --> 09:27.060
is the fake miniature realm.

09:27.560 --> 09:28.690
You are filled with hatred,

09:29.680 --> 09:31.450
dwelling in suspicion and wariness all the time,

09:32.280 --> 09:33.850
yet you dream of controlling heavenly law.

09:35.680 --> 09:36.490
Ridiculous.

09:39.470 --> 09:40.300
So what?

09:41.470 --> 09:43.660
No matter how well Qingcheng hid you,

09:44.510 --> 09:47.450
you shall end up in my hands.

09:57.990 --> 10:00.210
I'll refine you into a vessel

10:00.230 --> 10:01.420
and absorb all your spirit energy

10:02.110 --> 10:04.210
to become the supreme cultivator.

10:05.040 --> 10:07.330
Then I will unify all immortal sects,

10:07.350 --> 10:08.450
wipe out the demon clan,

10:08.560 --> 10:10.900
and rewrite the world's rules.

10:11.510 --> 10:12.420
As the saying goes,

10:12.920 --> 10:14.260
those who obey me shall thrive;

10:15.280 --> 10:16.780
those who oppose me shall perish.

10:39.230 --> 10:39.850
Cuixuan,

10:40.630 --> 10:42.690
dozens of immortal sects are breaking the barrier,

10:42.990 --> 10:44.020
claiming they wish to see the Divine Tree.

10:46.160 --> 10:47.940
How did they learn that?

10:50.960 --> 10:52.020
What one does,

10:52.990 --> 10:54.140
heaven witnesses.

10:58.320 --> 11:00.060
Do you think you can hide everything

11:01.040 --> 11:02.380
and control all under heaven?

11:28.470 --> 11:29.300
Elder Cuixuan,

11:30.040 --> 11:31.540
since the Divine Tree is in your possession,

11:31.560 --> 11:32.540
why keep it concealed?

11:33.280 --> 11:35.690
What do you plan to do with it next?

11:43.040 --> 11:44.300
Matters of the Wuyue Court

11:45.320 --> 11:47.570
hardly require any explanation to you.

11:49.280 --> 11:50.420
That's not how it works.

11:51.470 --> 11:52.780
The demon clan has run rampant lately.

11:53.230 --> 11:55.300
Many immortal cultivators have fallen victim.

11:55.990 --> 11:58.020
The Sea Calamity is also drawing near.

11:58.350 --> 11:59.610
The Divine Tree concerns the safety

11:59.630 --> 12:01.060
of every sect

12:01.080 --> 12:02.180
and the Central Plains.

12:02.470 --> 12:03.140
How can you claim

12:03.440 --> 12:04.780
it's only Wuyue Court's business?

12:05.320 --> 12:06.210
Am I right, everyone?

12:07.040 --> 12:07.900
- Yes. - Exactly!

12:07.920 --> 12:08.490
Yeah.

12:08.510 --> 12:09.940
In the wars against demons years ago,

12:10.590 --> 12:13.180
Dizang Sect's ancestors were wounded by the Divine Tree.

12:13.510 --> 12:15.300
It owes our sect a blood debt

12:15.870 --> 12:16.850
that cannot be ignored.

12:17.590 --> 12:18.210
True!

12:18.560 --> 12:20.090
The Divine Tree also harmed our ancestors.

12:20.680 --> 12:21.060
Right!

12:21.510 --> 12:22.970
We must stand united

12:23.160 --> 12:24.850
against this outsider.

12:25.400 --> 12:25.900
Indeed.

12:26.440 --> 12:27.540
We ought to deal with it together

12:27.800 --> 12:28.540
and discuss a solution side by side.

12:29.280 --> 12:30.180
Let's discuss a solution.

12:31.960 --> 12:33.140
Everyone, listen!

12:35.990 --> 12:37.690
You've all traveled far today.

12:38.080 --> 12:39.780
You may rest first.

12:39.800 --> 12:42.060
Word spreads that the Divine Tree colludes with the demon clan.

12:42.560 --> 12:43.850
Every day we delay

12:44.080 --> 12:45.690
brings greater peril.

12:46.320 --> 12:48.060
We must resolve this without delay.

12:50.710 --> 12:51.850
I share

12:52.800 --> 12:54.970
your worries.

12:56.440 --> 12:58.730
That is why I sealed all news

12:59.470 --> 13:00.850
and imprisoned the Divine Tree.

13:02.990 --> 13:03.610
Yet

13:04.200 --> 13:06.140
since you have gathered here,

13:06.630 --> 13:08.610
tomorrow, I shall hold a public trial

13:08.920 --> 13:10.940
of the Divine Tree with all of you.

13:12.160 --> 13:14.180
What do you say?

13:31.200 --> 13:32.020
Zhaomin.

13:40.990 --> 13:42.450
Elder Cuixuan has laid secret restriction spells

13:42.560 --> 13:43.660
all around the Wuyue Shrine.

13:44.510 --> 13:45.540
Do not force your way in.

13:46.830 --> 13:48.180
Later, Zhaomin and I

13:48.200 --> 13:49.540
will draw off the guards outside.

13:52.590 --> 13:53.780
Use this to slice open

13:53.800 --> 13:55.020
the barrier temporarily.

13:55.440 --> 13:57.300
But Elder Cuixuan will sense it for sure,

13:57.630 --> 13:58.610
so you must move fast.

13:59.400 --> 14:00.810
If you fail to rescue Lifei in time,

14:01.960 --> 14:02.730
retreat at once.

14:03.160 --> 14:03.940
We'll rethink our plan.

14:04.710 --> 14:06.850
Deng and I cannot openly defy our sect.

14:07.870 --> 14:08.970
We appreciate you risking your lives.

14:09.680 --> 14:11.210
Thank you both on behalf of Lifei.

14:11.800 --> 14:12.850
No need for formalities.

14:13.280 --> 14:14.330
Lifei is family to me.

14:14.350 --> 14:15.380
I'll save her no matter what.

14:15.710 --> 14:18.020
This is nothing like what happened in Duanming City.

14:18.350 --> 14:19.730
If Elder Cuixuan catches us,

14:20.080 --> 14:20.900
we'll be branded traitors

14:20.920 --> 14:22.300
colluding with outsiders,

14:22.630 --> 14:23.940
and we might even lose our lives.

14:24.680 --> 14:25.900
Last time in Duanming City,

14:26.160 --> 14:27.610
Lifei risked her life for the Jiufeng Clan.

14:28.160 --> 14:29.940
My clan always repays kindness.

14:32.110 --> 14:32.900
What about the Wanxian Sect?

14:34.400 --> 14:35.450
The Sea Sects have always been seen

14:35.470 --> 14:36.490
as outsiders by the Mountain Sects.

14:36.830 --> 14:38.330
My master approved our trip here.

14:38.830 --> 14:39.690
I don't mind getting dragged

14:39.800 --> 14:40.210
into trouble.

15:07.710 --> 15:11.540
Cuixuan must be troubled by those immortal sects.

15:14.200 --> 15:14.780
So,

15:16.400 --> 15:18.210
have you agreed on how to split my power?

15:20.470 --> 15:21.450
We'll decide what to do with you

15:21.800 --> 15:22.570
after the public trial tomorrow

15:23.040 --> 15:24.060
at Chen hour.

15:27.510 --> 15:28.090
I once

15:29.630 --> 15:31.180
asked you to be my cultivation partner

15:31.750 --> 15:32.780
and practice with me,

15:33.470 --> 15:34.850
yet you refused time and again.

15:36.630 --> 15:37.490
Never thought

15:38.710 --> 15:40.490
you'd end up like this today.

15:42.920 --> 15:45.940
I thought you still held old affection

15:45.960 --> 15:46.810
and came to see me.

15:48.110 --> 15:49.690
Turns out you're just here to gloat.

15:52.200 --> 15:53.730
I do have a lingering fondness for you.

15:54.960 --> 15:56.540
If you change your mind,

16:00.590 --> 16:02.450
I might take you away.

16:05.320 --> 16:06.570
Can you undo

16:08.080 --> 16:09.020
these chains on me?

16:16.200 --> 16:17.730
Seems we were never fated to be together.

16:18.680 --> 16:19.730
Since things cannot go as we wish,

16:21.080 --> 16:21.810
why not

16:23.320 --> 16:24.330
share some

16:24.350 --> 16:25.450
of your spirit energy with me?

16:29.160 --> 16:30.810
You also want my spirit energy?

16:33.040 --> 16:34.610
You're doomed anyway.

16:35.470 --> 16:37.450
Leave a trace of your energy for me.

16:41.710 --> 16:42.380
Very well.

16:44.630 --> 16:46.850
Better to give it to you

16:48.590 --> 16:49.610
than let that old villain Cuixuan seize it.

16:51.230 --> 16:52.780
You treated me kindly once, after all.

16:55.680 --> 16:56.300
Rest assured.

16:56.870 --> 16:58.090
I'll be gentle,

16:58.920 --> 17:00.570
and you won't suffer any pain.

17:10.550 --> 17:11.820
You worry too much.

17:12.880 --> 17:14.450
I'm bound by spirit-sealing chains,

17:15.840 --> 17:16.580
unable to move an inch.

17:17.600 --> 17:18.820
No need to be so cautious.

17:20.550 --> 17:22.050
You planned to use spirit absorption against me.

17:25.990 --> 17:27.490
Cunning as ever, Lifei.

17:28.160 --> 17:29.490
Death draws near,

17:29.510 --> 17:31.210
yet you still scheme against me.

17:32.160 --> 17:33.340
Then do not blame me

17:33.990 --> 17:35.490
for showing no mercy.

18:01.120 --> 18:01.690
What's this?

18:02.840 --> 18:04.380
You want the Divine Tree's power, right?

18:06.360 --> 18:06.900
Take it.

18:20.400 --> 18:21.010
Lifei!

18:21.030 --> 18:21.860
What brings you here?

18:25.600 --> 18:26.210
It won't work.

18:26.790 --> 18:27.450
Let me try again.

18:27.750 --> 18:28.380
There has to be a way.

18:35.510 --> 18:37.290
Even the Wuyue Court's treasures

18:38.030 --> 18:39.940
cannot break these chains.

18:41.030 --> 18:43.050
Better spare the effort.

18:46.030 --> 18:47.180
Useless fools!

18:47.840 --> 18:49.340
Out of respect for Mr. Shen,

18:49.880 --> 18:51.250
I shall spare your lives for now.

18:52.160 --> 18:53.660
You may stay and accompany her

18:54.120 --> 18:55.690
through her final moments.

19:16.360 --> 19:17.380
I've dragged you into trouble.

19:18.360 --> 19:19.580
Truth is, I'm...

19:19.600 --> 19:20.290
The Divine Tree.

19:21.510 --> 19:22.100
We already know.

19:25.960 --> 19:27.380
We suspected it back in Duantu.

19:28.790 --> 19:30.140
Tongzhou and Xiuyuan must have known, too.

19:30.790 --> 19:32.100
That's why they sent Miaoqing to stand in for you.

19:35.750 --> 19:36.970
So many have suffered because of me.

19:38.680 --> 19:39.340
Gelin,

19:40.360 --> 19:41.770
as you knew my identity all along,

19:42.680 --> 19:43.730
you never should have come.

19:44.400 --> 19:45.340
Don't talk nonsense.

19:45.840 --> 19:46.690
We knew each other young

19:46.710 --> 19:47.380
and walked through things together.

19:47.640 --> 19:48.660
Because you're the Divine Tree,

19:48.680 --> 19:49.860
you cease to be one of us?

19:51.160 --> 19:51.620
What?

19:52.070 --> 19:53.530
The Divine Tree looks down on us?

19:53.680 --> 19:55.050
Think we're not worthy to be your friends?

19:57.840 --> 19:59.010
We'll always be friends.

20:03.120 --> 20:03.860
I just...

20:03.880 --> 20:04.620
Don't worry.

20:05.230 --> 20:06.900
Chongyi and Zhaomin are working on a plan.

20:07.440 --> 20:08.660
We will get you out for sure.

20:10.880 --> 20:11.490
Where's Xiuyuan?

20:12.550 --> 20:14.100
I heard the demon clan took him hostage.

20:14.550 --> 20:15.620
Is his life in danger?

20:24.030 --> 20:24.770
He

20:26.440 --> 20:27.900
should be fine.

20:28.400 --> 20:29.820
With his cultivation and wits,

20:30.230 --> 20:31.450
he'll turn misfortune into safety.

20:31.790 --> 20:32.660
But what about you?

20:33.310 --> 20:34.290
Tomorrow's public trial

20:34.550 --> 20:35.380
will have every sect watching.

20:36.030 --> 20:36.690
No one knows

20:36.710 --> 20:37.380
what they'll do to you.

20:40.960 --> 20:42.420
I've been waiting for this trial.

21:13.790 --> 21:16.180
Disguising herself as the Chufeng Academy's disciple,

21:16.640 --> 21:17.860
the Divine Tree infiltrated the Wuyue Court

21:17.990 --> 21:19.100
with malicious schemes.

21:19.600 --> 21:22.530
I've found and captured her alive

21:23.230 --> 21:24.690
for this public trial.

21:40.680 --> 21:42.770
Fellow cultivators,

21:43.160 --> 21:44.660
do you have any questions?

21:57.400 --> 21:58.210
Immortal Cuixuan,

22:01.550 --> 22:03.730
I believe none of us will raise objections.

22:09.880 --> 22:10.380
Everyone,

22:11.600 --> 22:13.420
Lei Xiuyuan is a demon spy,

22:13.790 --> 22:15.250
and Jiang Lifei is equally guilty.

22:16.200 --> 22:18.140
In my opinion, no need for a trial.

22:18.840 --> 22:21.100
The Divine Tree must not remain in the world.

22:25.680 --> 22:27.050
Mr. Luo speaks the truth.

22:27.840 --> 22:29.820
The previous Divine Tree helped the Demon Lord Yecha

22:30.510 --> 22:33.010
slaughter countless cultivators.

22:33.510 --> 22:33.970
Today,

22:34.310 --> 22:35.820
we shall make her pay back

22:36.070 --> 22:37.010
every last debt she owes us.

22:38.710 --> 22:39.340
Exactly.

22:39.960 --> 22:41.340
Blood for blood.

22:43.200 --> 22:45.210
The Divine Tree draws boundless spirit energy

22:46.120 --> 22:47.210
from heaven and earth.

22:48.230 --> 22:48.820
I say

22:49.200 --> 22:51.340
we all absorb her energy together

22:51.510 --> 22:52.530
to boost our cultivation,

22:52.840 --> 22:53.620
fend off the Sea Calamity,

22:54.120 --> 22:55.210
and defeat the demon clan.

22:55.400 --> 23:04.210
Fend off the Sea Calamity! Defeat the demon clan!

23:04.230 --> 23:05.730
Enough!

23:07.920 --> 23:08.690
All of you!

23:49.600 --> 23:51.530
Can you all not contain your greed?

23:53.360 --> 23:55.730
The crimes of the old Divine Tree are not hers to bear.

23:56.120 --> 23:57.340
In White Cliff and Duanming City,

23:57.360 --> 23:58.730
Lifei only saved lives.

23:59.070 --> 24:01.210
She has never harmed a single innocent soul,

24:01.990 --> 24:02.820
and every one of you

24:03.600 --> 24:05.490
knows this full well.

24:12.750 --> 24:13.420
What is this?

24:14.160 --> 24:16.620
Just because she bears the Divine Tree's power,

24:17.400 --> 24:18.860
you seek to plunder her spiritual energy

24:18.880 --> 24:20.380
without distinguishing right from wrong?

24:21.510 --> 24:22.660
If that is your intent,

24:23.360 --> 24:24.290
let me ask you all.

24:26.310 --> 24:27.290
How are you any different

24:28.750 --> 24:30.340
from the demon clan?

24:31.120 --> 24:31.450
You...

24:40.840 --> 24:41.940
The Sea Calamity shall ruin the world,

24:42.440 --> 24:43.490
and the innocents will perish.

24:44.640 --> 24:45.690
Capturing the Divine Tree

24:46.310 --> 24:47.730
is heaven's blessing,

24:48.550 --> 24:51.900
a sign that this power is meant to serve us.

24:52.960 --> 24:55.730
We must not cling to misplaced mercy

24:56.270 --> 24:58.050
and waste the blessing.

24:58.960 --> 25:00.580
Immortal Cuixuan speaks the truth.

25:00.960 --> 25:02.530
We must follow heaven's will,

25:03.070 --> 25:03.860
slay the Divine Tree,

25:04.160 --> 25:05.050
and absorb her spirit energy!

25:05.550 --> 25:16.420
Slay the Divine Tree! Absorb her energy!

25:16.440 --> 25:16.900
Ridiculous.

25:16.920 --> 25:17.690
Absorb my energy?

25:20.470 --> 25:21.860
You're all absurd.

25:23.270 --> 25:24.010
Insolent witch!

25:24.550 --> 25:26.050
Your end draws near. What's so funny?

25:34.640 --> 25:36.250
I laugh at your naivety.

25:37.360 --> 25:38.580
Do you believe Cuixuan will share

25:38.600 --> 25:39.970
my energy with all of you?

25:42.030 --> 25:43.450
How blind can you be?

25:46.840 --> 25:47.450
Witch,

25:48.070 --> 25:49.580
cease your deceitful words to sow discord!

25:49.990 --> 25:51.580
Immortal Cuixuan is noble and selfless,

25:51.710 --> 25:52.690
devoted to the greater good.

25:53.230 --> 25:54.490
Never try to sow discord.

25:56.710 --> 25:57.580
The greater good?

26:00.400 --> 26:01.970
Do you see these chains binding me?

26:10.120 --> 26:10.770
Jiang Lifei,

26:11.710 --> 26:13.140
these chains look extraordinary.

26:13.840 --> 26:14.770
What is the story behind them?

26:16.070 --> 26:16.970
Lady Longjing,

26:18.550 --> 26:19.730
you once aided me

26:20.680 --> 26:22.050
and have seen through many things.

26:22.880 --> 26:24.250
I'll tell you the truth out of goodwill.

26:27.510 --> 26:28.820
Cuixuan designed

26:31.640 --> 26:33.900
these dragon-binding spirit-sealing chains solely to subdue

26:33.920 --> 26:34.860
my master Qingcheng.

26:36.920 --> 26:38.690
They have fused deep into my bones and blood.

26:41.960 --> 26:43.820
If you absorb my spirit energy,

26:44.600 --> 26:47.730
the sealing spell will transfer into your bodies.

26:48.360 --> 26:49.010
Then each of you

26:50.990 --> 26:53.010
will become Cuixuan's puppets.

26:59.960 --> 27:01.380
Devious witch!

27:01.510 --> 27:03.010
You're misleading everyone.

27:05.360 --> 27:06.100
Don't trust

27:06.270 --> 27:06.940
a monster's lies.

27:07.960 --> 27:09.050
We are fellow immortal cultivators.

27:09.600 --> 27:11.210
Why would I harm any of you?

27:12.030 --> 27:14.180
Because you want to stand supreme under heaven.

27:14.680 --> 27:15.660
Driven by this ambition,

27:16.990 --> 27:19.180
you murdered your senior brother Qingcheng,

27:20.360 --> 27:21.860
consorted with demons,

27:23.200 --> 27:24.660
and drained stray spirits from foreign lands.

27:25.600 --> 27:26.900
There is no evil you would not commit.

27:32.600 --> 27:34.250
Now that you possess me,

27:34.990 --> 27:36.380
you'd never share my energy with others.

27:39.600 --> 27:41.380
Qingcheng is dead?

27:48.680 --> 27:49.450
He perished

27:51.840 --> 27:53.970
in Cuixuan's miniature realm.

27:57.470 --> 27:58.820
You may verify this

27:59.960 --> 28:01.900
at his former residence on Hushe Peak.

28:02.310 --> 28:02.940
Cuixuan,

28:03.750 --> 28:05.250
was what she said the truth?

28:10.440 --> 28:10.940
Guangwei,

28:11.600 --> 28:13.420
do not believe her slander.

28:16.990 --> 28:17.580
Witch,

28:17.960 --> 28:19.380
stop clouding our judgment.

28:19.790 --> 28:21.010
Do you think sowing discord among us

28:21.230 --> 28:22.420
will spare your life?

28:41.270 --> 28:42.250
Zhaomin,

28:44.920 --> 28:45.900
I'm thirsty.

28:58.310 --> 28:59.100
Watch out, it's a trap!

29:27.470 --> 29:28.100
Qingcheng.

29:29.200 --> 29:29.770
Qingcheng.

29:32.960 --> 29:34.420
Qingcheng!

29:39.470 --> 29:41.450
If they saw you kill my master

29:42.310 --> 29:44.340
and piles of bones in the miniature realm,

29:44.840 --> 29:46.490
would they still buy your lies?

29:46.960 --> 29:49.290
The miniature realm has been destroyed.

29:50.440 --> 29:51.580
No one will believe a word

29:51.680 --> 29:53.140
of what you say.

30:00.920 --> 30:05.770
I've long heard that Qingcheng's Senluo Grand Art

30:06.200 --> 30:07.420
can trace back to past events.

30:09.360 --> 30:11.290
So she is really his disciple.

30:16.400 --> 30:18.620
I'll refine you into a vessel

30:18.640 --> 30:19.730
and absorb all your spirit energy

30:20.400 --> 30:22.690
to become the supreme cultivator.

30:23.070 --> 30:25.050
Then I will unify all immortal sects,

30:25.070 --> 30:26.140
wipe out the demon clan,

30:26.360 --> 30:28.660
and rewrite the world's rules.

30:28.790 --> 30:29.530
As the saying goes,

30:30.680 --> 30:32.050
those who obey me shall thrive;

30:32.550 --> 30:33.940
those who oppose me shall perish.

30:38.880 --> 30:39.660
Why?

30:41.030 --> 30:43.050
Why did you kill Qingcheng?

30:43.840 --> 30:46.820
You two used to be the closest friends.

30:49.070 --> 30:51.100
He colluded with monsters

30:51.510 --> 30:52.660
and sheltered demons,

30:53.200 --> 30:54.860
making him a traitor to all immortal sects.

30:55.200 --> 30:56.940
I had every right

30:56.960 --> 30:57.730
to slay him.

31:00.880 --> 31:02.140
You killed him,

31:03.840 --> 31:06.490
so I will avenge him!

31:07.270 --> 31:07.900
Chongyi.

31:08.230 --> 31:08.900
- Let me go! - Cuixuan.

31:08.920 --> 31:09.770
- Calm your rage. - Release me!

31:10.360 --> 31:11.050
Let go of me!

31:11.070 --> 31:11.770
Facing the Sea Calamity,

31:12.030 --> 31:12.900
don't turn on one another.

31:13.160 --> 31:14.250
We care nothing

31:14.750 --> 31:16.010
for your sect's feuds

31:16.470 --> 31:17.580
over Qingcheng.

31:18.070 --> 31:20.050
Today, we must absorb the Divine Tree's power.

31:20.070 --> 31:20.660
Exactly.

31:21.270 --> 31:23.940
The Divine Tree will only bring disasters.

31:24.070 --> 31:24.860
I say

31:24.880 --> 31:26.660
we consume her power together.

31:32.750 --> 31:36.140
You think you can absorb the power?

31:44.310 --> 31:46.690
All those peerless, extraordinary talents

31:47.310 --> 31:49.580
perished centuries ago.

31:50.160 --> 31:52.690
Only mediocre folk like you remain,

31:53.030 --> 31:55.210
occupying positions yet accomplishing nothing.

31:56.440 --> 31:58.420
For you to absorb the power

31:59.200 --> 32:00.770
is akin to burning lutes to cook cranes,

32:00.790 --> 32:01.860
a waste of divine treasure.

32:02.600 --> 32:04.900
Far better to channel all its power into me alone.

32:05.790 --> 32:07.010
With my strength,

32:07.710 --> 32:09.210
I can withstand the Sea Calamity

32:09.510 --> 32:10.820
and wipe out the demon clan.

32:11.160 --> 32:12.250
Have you lost your mind?

32:13.200 --> 32:13.820
Cuixuan,

32:14.160 --> 32:15.490
you're talking nonsense.

32:16.160 --> 32:16.770
Guangwei,

32:17.640 --> 32:19.690
you were gravely wounded by Yecha,

32:20.360 --> 32:22.380
stunting your cultivation forever.

32:22.880 --> 32:25.580
Don't you wish to wipe away this humiliation?

32:25.960 --> 32:27.450
I stand irreconcilably against the demon clan.

32:27.840 --> 32:29.290
Yet all you've done

32:29.400 --> 32:30.690
is no different from them.

32:31.400 --> 32:33.690
You are stubborn beyond reasoning.

32:33.710 --> 32:34.180
You...

32:35.710 --> 32:36.290
Cuixuan,

32:36.550 --> 32:37.210
turn back

32:37.230 --> 32:38.380
while there is still time.

32:40.510 --> 32:41.620
What are you trying to do?

32:47.030 --> 32:48.730
Move aside.

32:49.310 --> 32:50.010
Move aside!

32:59.600 --> 33:00.900
The Divine Tree belongs to the Lantian Sect!

33:00.920 --> 33:02.050
No, it belongs to the Dizang Sect!

33:02.750 --> 33:04.620
- Seize it! - Hurry, move!

33:04.880 --> 33:06.620
- Hurry. - Go after her!

33:06.840 --> 33:07.420
Protect Lifei!

33:08.470 --> 33:09.420
The Divine Tree is ours!

33:13.680 --> 33:14.450
Stay back!

33:14.600 --> 33:15.380
Guard Lifei at all costs!

33:15.640 --> 33:16.210
Stay back!

33:17.470 --> 33:18.380
The Divine Tree is ours.

33:19.200 --> 33:19.770
She is ours!

33:20.070 --> 33:21.210
Don't fight us for her.

33:22.070 --> 33:23.660
No one can take her from us!

33:26.070 --> 33:26.730
Move aside!

33:27.200 --> 33:27.730
Step away!

33:42.310 --> 33:43.450
Hand her over to us.

33:43.880 --> 33:44.620
She's ours!

33:54.920 --> 33:56.050
She is ours.

33:56.070 --> 33:57.250
She belongs to our sect!

33:58.310 --> 33:59.530
She's ours!

34:00.710 --> 34:01.530
Step aside!

34:04.200 --> 34:04.820
Ours.

34:04.920 --> 34:05.820
Master,

34:07.510 --> 34:09.820
are they the ones you swore to protect?

34:11.990 --> 34:13.860
- Move aside! - This treasure is ours!

34:15.240 --> 34:16.260
She's ours.

34:19.880 --> 34:20.530
Lifei!

34:21.800 --> 34:22.420
Lifei!

34:23.550 --> 34:24.610
The Divine Tree is ours.

34:24.630 --> 34:25.900
She is ours.

34:29.590 --> 34:31.820
- Give her to me! - Move aside!

34:34.440 --> 34:35.940
The Divine Tree belongs to our sect!

34:36.030 --> 34:37.220
Master,

34:38.920 --> 34:40.610
I've done all I could.

34:42.360 --> 34:44.570
- Give her to me! - Now!

35:10.470 --> 35:11.130
Demonic energy!

35:11.240 --> 35:12.420
Channel your cultivation to resist it!

35:47.390 --> 35:50.920
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

35:51.590 --> 35:53.960
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

35:54.280 --> 35:57.480
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds, break through the waves♪

35:58.080 --> 36:00.360
♪The heart's ocean knows no shore♪

36:00.760 --> 36:04.480
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

36:05.120 --> 36:07.520
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

36:07.960 --> 36:11.120
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water♪

36:11.720 --> 36:14.080
♪And falling petals♪

36:14.800 --> 36:19.070
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪

36:20.400 --> 36:21.010
Xiuyuan?

36:22.400 --> 36:23.610
So he is the one

36:24.070 --> 36:24.900
with golden eyes.

36:25.670 --> 36:26.900
Xiuyuan is Yecha?

36:28.190 --> 36:28.940
Divine Lord?

36:39.670 --> 36:40.700
What scent is this?

36:41.720 --> 36:44.220
Qingcheng sealed her origin

36:45.070 --> 36:46.380
to hide her spirit aura.

36:47.400 --> 36:49.900
Now she is regaining her Divine Tree physique.

37:01.590 --> 37:02.300
I'll take you away.

37:32.760 --> 37:33.490
Yecha,

37:34.030 --> 37:35.090
meet your end!

38:13.840 --> 38:14.530
Cuixuan,

38:15.590 --> 38:17.380
the five-century feud between you

38:19.190 --> 38:20.380
and my clan ends today.

38:54.070 --> 38:55.130
Who dares seize my Divine Tree?

38:57.920 --> 38:58.490
Xiuyuan!

39:05.190 --> 39:05.860
Are you alright?

39:20.320 --> 39:21.340
You said

39:24.630 --> 39:26.170
you'd always be Lei Xiuyuan.

39:27.960 --> 39:29.090
Have you forgotten it?

40:33.320 --> 40:34.490
Five centuries have passed.

40:35.470 --> 40:37.700
My clan shall finally wipe out all immortal sects.

40:39.110 --> 40:40.900
The Fruit of the Divine Tree is within your grasp.

40:42.150 --> 40:43.900
My Lord, please enjoy it.

40:52.440 --> 40:53.220
Xiuyuan.

41:13.190 --> 41:14.090
Lei Xiuyuan!

41:26.280 --> 41:30.260
Don't forget the original intent of your practice.

42:33.280 --> 42:34.740
It ends like this again.

42:36.320 --> 42:37.050
Is this

42:37.510 --> 42:38.780
truly the end?

42:42.050 --> 42:42.360
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:42.360 --> 42:44.560
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

42:57.500 --> 43:01.020
♪The warmth within my arms♪

43:01.180 --> 43:04.700
♪I can no longer hold on to♪

43:04.820 --> 43:08.340
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

43:08.460 --> 43:11.940
♪Keep you warm until sunrise?♪

43:11.940 --> 43:15.580
♪My heartbeat freezes♪

43:15.980 --> 43:19.260
♪I can no longer tell you♪

43:19.380 --> 43:22.900
♪Looking you in the eyes, I cannot♪

43:22.940 --> 43:25.940
♪Utter that line♪

43:26.100 --> 43:28.140
♪Knowing love and hate♪

43:28.220 --> 43:32.620
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

43:33.340 --> 43:35.420
♪I still linger on♪

43:35.580 --> 43:39.860
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

43:40.020 --> 43:44.540
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

43:44.620 --> 43:48.140
♪But we thought nothing of it♪

43:48.220 --> 43:51.660
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

43:51.940 --> 43:55.180
♪I wish you well♪

43:55.340 --> 43:57.060
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

43:57.220 --> 44:01.900
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

44:02.500 --> 44:04.580
♪You're still screaming♪

44:04.740 --> 44:09.220
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

44:09.340 --> 44:13.820
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

44:14.060 --> 44:17.020
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

44:17.140 --> 44:19.020
♪Leaping straight into♪

44:19.140 --> 44:23.900
♪That heartbreaking past♪

44:24.140 --> 44:27.660
♪Just to keep you safe♪

44:34.100 --> 44:37.420
♪My breath is about to stop♪

44:37.540 --> 44:41.060
♪Those hands can no longer hold yours♪

44:41.180 --> 44:44.620
♪Through the future snow, wind, and fog♪

44:44.780 --> 44:47.980
♪Who will be there by your side?♪

44:48.100 --> 44:51.820
♪I smile as it ends♪

44:51.980 --> 44:55.620
♪Afraid that you might cry for me♪

44:55.820 --> 44:59.220
♪Quietly, I turn into a sky lantern♪

44:59.380 --> 45:02.500
♪To light your way through the night♪

45:02.580 --> 45:04.620
♪Knowing love and hate♪

45:04.700 --> 45:09.100
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

45:09.860 --> 45:11.900
♪I still linger on♪

45:12.060 --> 45:16.340
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

45:16.500 --> 45:21.020
♪The storm looms, yet I stand in its way♪

45:21.100 --> 45:24.300
♪Torn inside, still I burn bright♪

45:24.500 --> 45:26.460
♪With the light from my fingertips♪

45:26.540 --> 45:30.940
♪I build a paradise♪

45:31.100 --> 45:34.580
♪To wander with you♪
